License:        LGPLv2+ and LGPLv2
URL:            http://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/

Source0:        http://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/src/gst-plugins-bad/gst-plugins-bad-%{version}.tar.xz

BuildRequires:  freedesktop-sdk-base
